@100 =~Sylvan Mystic Kit, by Polar Bear~
@101 =~sylvan mystic~
@102 =~Sylvan Mystic~
@103 =~SYLVAN MYSTIC: The Sylvan Mystics are an ancient order of Elven and Half-Elven Rangers in Faer√ªn. They specialize in hunting evil mages and mind flayers, and as such they must attune their mind in addition to their body.

Advantages:
- Gains a +1 bonus to Armor Class, damage and THAC0 at 1st level.
- Gains a -1 Weapon Speed every 5 levels.
- May cast Dispel Magic and True Sight as innate abilities.
- May cast Chaotic Commands and Iron Skin as innate abilities. Gains one use at level at level 9.
- May cast Aura of Flaming Death as innate ability. Gains one use at level at level 21.
- May cast Summon Deva as innate ability. Gains one use at level at level 23.

Disadvantages:
- Incurs a penalty to Strength (-5) and Constitution (-4).
- May not use the Charm Animal ability.
- May only use bows and bladed weapons.
- May not wear armor heavier than chain mail.
- Race restricted to half-elf or elf.
- Alignment restricted to lawful or neutral good.~
