This spell creates a blackish glow around the caster's hands. This glow gives the caster a +1 THAC0 plus an additional +1 THAC0 for every three levels of the caster up to a maximum of +7 at level 19. After level 20, the spell's duration stays at 24 rounds. This spell is almost always used in association with any of the spells that cause the caster to touch the target to complete the spell effect, like Shocking Grasp and Vampiric Touch.~
